text: A video shared on Instagram claims an Executive Order from President Joe Biden will purportedly replace cash with digital currency by December 2022.
entity_strings: December 2022, Executive Order, Instagram, digital currency

text: Executive Order 14067, signed by President Joe Biden, replaces the U.S. dollar with traceable digital currency that will eliminate constitutional liberties like freedom and privacy.
